Story*
One upon a time, there lived a monkey on a jamoon tree which was at the bank of a river.
In the same forest there lived a crocodile and its wife.
ONe day the crocodile came the bank of the river a rested under the jamoon tree.
And the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits.
The crocodile ate and liked them very much.
Day passed and they became good friends.
One day monkey send some friuts to crocodile's wife.
The crocodile's wife tasted the friuts but wanted to eat monkey's hearted